[SPEAKER_01] U biti, moji kolači košto ja sve radim, radim ih u silikonskih kalupima.

868
00:39:43,000 --> 00:39:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da ja njih, zapravo, planski sve radim kad radim normative.

869
00:39:46,000 --> 00:39:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da, da.

870
00:39:47,000 --> 00:39:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] Točno se radi da uvijek da nema tu prešta.

871
00:39:49,000 --> 00:39:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] A mislio sam ove kada je baka, pekla, poni, okreć i ostalo.

872
00:39:52,000 --> 00:39:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] A to je drugo, to se izrezuje.

873
00:39:53,000 --> 00:39:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] Meni se kolači u kalupima, tako da svaki sad nema izrezivanje, nema tu zapravo osataka.

874
00:39:57,000 --> 00:39:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znači ti šure baš slasičarnicu otvorite.

875
00:39:59,000 --> 00:40:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] Neće biti ono suhi keksi za svadbe.

876
00:40:02,000 --> 00:40:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] A bit će, bit će, moraš, ali opet drugačije.

877
00:40:04,000 --> 00:40:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da, da, da.

878
00:40:05,000 --> 00:40:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da, mora biti ono kako bi se reklo malo.

879
00:40:07,000 --> 00:40:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja gledam da treba biti inovetivan.

880
00:40:09,000 --> 00:40:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znači ne želim se ponavljati, ili ok, ako radiš nešto što je, ono, svi rade, opet napraviti nešto da bude tvoje.

881
00:40:17,000 --> 00:40:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] Stavi svoj podpis, par ja to ko gledam.

882
00:40:20,000 --> 00:40:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, slasičarstvo je odlična struka, možeš se izraziti.

883
00:40:26,000 --> 00:40:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] Samo, samo daj ideje, daj volje i daj nešto svoje.

884
00:40:29,000 --> 00:40:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

885
00:40:30,000 --> 00:40:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] Daj nešto svoje, stavi nešto da ljudi prepoznat da je to tvoj rad ili da je tvoj...

886
00:40:36,000 --> 00:40:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tvoj touch, tvoj pečet, da.

887
00:40:39,000 --> 00:40:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tvoj touch, tvoj touch, moraš možda što dodat.

888
00:40:41,000 --> 00:40:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

889
00:40:42,000 --> 00:40:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jure, šta ti radiš kad ne radiš?

890
00:40:45,000 --> 00:40:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim, ja sam pročitao.

891
00:40:46,000 --> 00:40:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jel imaš opše vremena za sebe?

892
00:40:48,000 --> 00:40:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] Žena, djeca, obitelj?

893
00:40:49,000 --> 00:40:51,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nemam, nemam, nemam, nemam ništa od toga.

894
00:40:51,000 --> 00:40:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] Cure, slobodan je, evo ga.

895
00:40:52,000 --> 00:40:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] Slobodan sam, da, da, slobodan sam.

896
00:40:55,000 --> 00:40:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] Otvoren je za sve opcije.

897
00:40:59,000 --> 00:41:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] Otvoren je za sve opcije.

898
00:41:00,000 --> 00:41:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] Klasika, klasika.

899
00:41:01,000 --> 00:41:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sko svaki dorbal i šta znam, ono, 27 godine.

900
00:41:05,000 --> 00:41:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] 27 godine.

901
00:41:07,000 --> 00:41:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sad već 27 godine mi zvuči puno.

902
00:41:09,000 --> 00:41:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] Prije dvije godine, 25, sam više bio i imam 20.

903
00:41:13,000 --> 00:41:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bobe sa 27, već mi je 30, a tu nije baš sve jedno.

904
00:41:17,000 --> 00:41:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] A gledaj.

905
00:41:18,000 --> 00:41:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nije sve jedno, ali, šta radim?

906
00:41:20,000 --> 00:41:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ma klasika.

907
00:41:21,000 --> 00:41:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali.

908
00:41:22,000 --> 00:41:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ko si normalni.

909
00:41:23,000 --> 00:41:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znam da voliš sport, jako da.

910
00:41:24,000 --> 00:41:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako, sport to božno.

911
00:41:25,000 --> 00:41:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pratim nogomet.

912
00:41:28,000 --> 00:41:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] Klasika, čitanje novina, ono.

913
00:41:31,000 --> 00:41:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kakvi su bili arsenalvi navijači? Mirni?

914
00:41:34,000 --> 00:41:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] Mirni, Mirni.

915
00:41:35,000 --> 00:41:38,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tamo je, ja, očišlo navijanje pri dvoje zvorena.

916
00:41:38,000 --> 00:41:39,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nema više.

917
00:41:39,000 --> 00:41:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ti se ni stadi ni rodije, to je gospođa Tačar Sredela.

918
00:41:41,000 --> 00:41:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] Samo na početku utakmice, ono, kaj bude.

919
00:41:43,000 --> 00:41:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da, to je gospođa Tačar Sredela.

920
00:41:46,000 --> 00:41:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ti se ni rodio, ni tonac rodio.

921
00:41:50,000 --> 00:41:51,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa tako nekako, da.

922
00:41:51,000 --> 00:41:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] Bok onih gluposti prije 80-ih.

923
00:41:53,000 --> 00:41:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali uglavnom, da, kao ono, klasika.

924
00:41:55,000 --> 00:41:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] Moje slobodno vrijeme je doslovno.

925
00:41:58,000 --> 00:42:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] I kad ti dolaze, cure, nek ne nose čokolade za poklonje.

926
00:42:02,000 --> 00:42:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da, da, da, da.

927
00:42:04,000 --> 00:42:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nisem nema smisla tebi dones čokoladu kuša.

928
00:42:07,000 --> 00:42:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da, to nikako.

929
00:42:09,000 --> 00:42:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jure, šta bih ko mladi urbani poduzetnik

930
00:42:14,000 --> 00:42:18,000
[SPEAKER_00] poručio svim tim tvoje generacije.

931
00:42:18,000 --> 00:42:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] Je teško, ali...

932
00:42:19,000 --> 00:42:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ništa, borite se.

933
00:42:20,000 --> 00:42:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] Borite se, grizite.

934
00:42:22,000 --> 00:42:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja isto prvi sam, kad sam kretuo, kad sam ovaj kretuo projekt,

935
00:42:28,000 --> 00:42:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] triput sam si rekao, da li bi ovo trebalo u životu?

936
00:42:31,000 --> 00:42:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] A da, otos.

937
00:42:32,000 --> 00:42:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da li bi ovo trebalo u životu?

938
00:42:34,000 --> 00:42:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] I na kraju se isplatilo.

939
00:42:36,000 --> 00:42:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bilo je teško, bilo je dana kad sam htio nazvat poslovne partnje,

940
00:42:39,000 --> 00:42:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] reći se otkazujem sve, ali ono, zagrizeš to i to krenuo si i u to ideš do kraja, guraš.

941
00:42:43,000 --> 00:42:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nama nazad, da.

942
00:42:44,000 --> 00:42:45,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nije, nije jednostavno.

943
00:42:45,000 --> 00:42:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim, sve je to, pogotovo kad više nove stvari, strah te je.

944
00:42:48,000 --> 00:42:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

945
00:42:49,000 --> 00:42:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nije te, ono, ne ideš sa sam uvjerajom, sto posto proći će.

946
00:42:52,000 --> 00:42:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

947
00:42:53,000 --> 00:42:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim, meni isto čisti primjer, gledam, ono, ne znam,

948
00:42:57,000 --> 00:42:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] ispro...

949
00:42:58,000 --> 00:42:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] U novom sam sam nečem našao.

950
00:42:59,000 --> 00:43:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ajmo reći.

951
00:43:00,000 --> 00:43:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] Prvi put sam s svojim imenom i prezimenom sam imao na kućici i ono.

952
00:43:04,000 --> 00:43:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bilo mi je najvažnije da se ja ne obrkam na način taj da bude loš proizvod, tako nešto.

953
00:43:09,000 --> 00:43:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ispalo je odlično.

954
00:43:10,000 --> 00:43:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali moglo je ispati kontra.

955
00:43:12,000 --> 00:43:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] A da, dobro.

956
00:43:13,000 --> 00:43:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] Moglo je.

957
00:43:14,000 --> 00:43:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali nije.

958
00:43:15,000 --> 00:43:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam vjerovao da će bit to dobro.

959
00:43:17,000 --> 00:43:18,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

960
00:43:18,000 --> 00:43:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] Poanta je ljudi nemoći se bojati.

961
00:43:19,000 --> 00:43:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da, nemoći se bojati.

962
00:43:20,000 --> 00:43:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jer nije ni u Njemačkoj sjajnoj, ni u Irskoj.

963
00:43:22,000 --> 00:43:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] Naravno, treba probati, treba pokušati.

964
00:43:24,000 --> 00:43:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da, pokušati.

965
00:43:25,000 --> 00:43:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] Moraš imat dozu straha, naravno, ali moraš imat dozu volje za uspjeho.

966
00:43:31,000 --> 00:43:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

967
00:43:32,000 --> 00:43:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nemaš volje, nećeš utpjeti.

968
00:43:33,000 --> 00:43:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] Moraš vjerovati u taj proizvod.

969
00:43:34,000 --> 00:43:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

970
00:43:35,000 --> 00:43:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja znam, ja sam bio siguran u svoj proizvod, ali nisam bio siguran kakav će biti reakcija, kak će to ić.

971
00:43:39,000 --> 00:43:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nakon tri dana sam ja prvi vikend kad smo videli kako to ide, nismo znali da smo mi, ono, super posao odradili.

972
00:43:47,000 --> 00:43:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

973
00:43:48,000 --> 00:43:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] I tek tamo, ja sam tek tamo nakon Božića shvatio šta se sve izdešao.

974
00:43:52,000 --> 00:43:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja nisam bio svjestan svega što se izdešavalo jer sam bio okupiran poslom, nisam stigao razmišljati.

975
00:43:57,000 --> 00:44:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja nisam vidio redove, ti nijednostavno ne percepiraš šta se dešava, koliko posla ima i kakav sam posao napravi, svi zajedno skupa, na kraju cijeli tim.

976
00:44:07,000 --> 00:44:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jer na kraju krajava, bez tima je ništa jer pojedinac, jedinka je ništa.

977
00:44:12,000 --> 00:44:13,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

978
00:44:13,000 --> 00:44:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je moje prvo, ja uvijek gledam da tim bude, da ljudi s kojima radim da mi budu, da bude interesantno, zabavno, šaljevo, ali opet da se odradi posao.

979
00:44:21,000 --> 00:44:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] I evo pred kraj smo, rekao si držat ćeš edukacije pa možda da upoznaš.

980
00:44:26,000 --> 00:44:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da, to je još neka, to je još neka, ajmo reć, zamisao, ali jako Bog da i plan.

981
00:44:35,000 --> 00:44:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] Isto još plan imamo mi, kakve planove sa tim Gdje je Jura?

982
00:44:39,000 --> 00:44:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako je, da.

983
00:44:41,000 --> 00:44:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dači, plana mi je za neki putopis po Hrvatskoj, to bude neka ekskluziva, to je neki plan, ali vidjet ćemo sad još, to je ono, planiramo ići po Hrvatskoj i nuditi neki bolji gastrodoživljaj.

984
00:44:53,000 --> 00:44:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] Evo dođite odmah kod nas, otvorite torneju.

985
00:44:56,000 --> 00:44:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa imamo još upita.

986
00:44:58,000 --> 00:45:03,000
[SPEAKER_00] Dobar je, dobar.

987
00:45:03,000 --> 00:45:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] jedini.

988
00:45:04,000 --> 00:45:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znam da nismo, ali moraš se gurat čovjek, laktarica.

989
00:45:06,000 --> 00:45:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] Naravno, naravno, naravno.

990
00:45:07,000 --> 00:45:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jure, cijeli dan si radio, bio si Frci, nećete dugo davit.

991
00:45:11,000 --> 00:45:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da, da, da, evo jedva gledam još tek mogu, da moram pogledati.

992
00:45:14,000 --> 00:45:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ti, da, u devetju, koliko je.

993
00:45:17,000 --> 00:45:18,000
[SPEAKER_00] U devetju, da.

994
00:45:18,000 --> 00:45:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] Možemo sam kratko, ok, ići ću u jedan, sedmog, drugog, ali naši rukomitači su bili u polufinalu, jesu?

995
00:45:24,000 --> 00:45:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jesu?

996
00:45:25,000 --> 00:45:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jesu, nisam.

997
00:45:26,000 --> 00:45:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja jesam?

998
00:45:27,000 --> 00:45:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nisam, nažalost nisam jer sam zaspao i napokon sam se raspavao.

999
00:45:30,000 --> 00:45:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] Aj, dobro, prošteno ti je.

1000
00:45:33,000 --> 00:45:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali bi žao, žao mi, jer nisam gledao, ali može bolje da nisam gledao jer možda ne bi dobili.

1001
00:45:38,000 --> 00:45:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] To neću, to neću ulaziti.

1002
00:45:40,000 --> 00:45:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da, hvala Boga, neću se dobili i to je to.

1003
00:45:42,000 --> 00:45:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, ideš sedmog, drugog, pa kako bilo, dečki, svaka vam čast, polufinalu ste bili, sad dićite, ne znam.

1004
00:45:48,000 --> 00:45:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znam se da će biti u finalu.

1005
00:45:49,000 --> 00:45:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da, da, svi se nadamo. Dinamo se isto nadamo da će biti sedmog.

1006
00:45:54,000 --> 00:45:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] Samo što se opet sa Francuzima.

1007
00:45:55,000 --> 00:45:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da, znam, da.

1008
00:45:56,000 --> 00:45:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] Oni si na crna mačka, to je baš.

1009
00:46:00,000 --> 00:46:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] Veliki brojeva da jednom kuži.

1010
00:46:02,000 --> 00:46:03,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ha, valjda će proći.

1011
00:46:03,000 --> 00:46:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znaš šta, možda ovo je ekipa mlađa.

1012
00:46:05,000 --> 00:46:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] Zna vi za Francuzi, ali možda nema onaj kompleks.

1013
00:46:08,000 --> 00:46:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ova generacija prije već imala kompleks.

1014
00:46:11,000 --> 00:46:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pusti to, ja mislim da to opet tu na plećima stoji.

1015
00:46:15,000 --> 00:46:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] Aj, čučemo se mi u nedelju.

1016
00:46:19,000 --> 00:46:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] Može, može, može.

1017
00:46:21,000 --> 00:46:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jure, hvala ti puno. Znam da si 18 sati dnevno na nogama, da si ovo, ono, hvala ti puno.

1018
00:46:26,000 --> 00:46:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jesam, jesam dosta sa veđirom.

1019
00:46:28,000 --> 00:46:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] Malo Karlu koji te i dofuro.

1020
00:46:29,000 --> 00:46:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

1021
00:46:30,000 --> 00:46:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da, tako da.

1022
00:46:31,000 --> 00:46:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] Treba nekad malo sati odmoriti oplanirati, malo sati odmoriti.

1023
00:46:33,000 --> 00:46:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] Je, je.

1024
00:46:34,000 --> 00:46:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] Malo jesam odmorio se, ali još, vidi šta, treba i raditi.

1025
00:46:38,000 --> 00:46:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tek treba sad i za...

1026
00:46:39,000 --> 00:46:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] Samo nađi dobar balans.

1027
00:46:40,000 --> 00:46:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

1028
00:46:41,000 --> 00:46:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] Vidim, ja tiš uspjet, ne, ne, to je zagarantirano.

1029
00:46:44,000 --> 00:46:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja se dadem.

1030
00:46:45,000 --> 00:46:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja se dadem.

1031
00:46:46,000 --> 00:46:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ne hebe tebe puno toga u životu.

1032
00:46:48,000 --> 00:46:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] Je, je, je, je.

1033
00:46:49,000 --> 00:46:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] Malo ja volim, volim.

1034
00:46:50,000 --> 00:46:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nije problem raditi, samo trebaš raditi ono što voliš.

1035
00:46:53,000 --> 00:46:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako je.

1036
00:46:54,000 --> 00:46:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] I onda ćeš biti sretan.

1037
00:46:55,000 --> 00:46:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jure, idemo se malo refreša dole i...

1038
00:46:57,000 --> 00:46:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] Može.

1039
00:46:58,000 --> 00:46:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ekipa, čao.

1040
00:46:59,000 --> 00:47:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] Čao, bok.

1041
00:47:11,000 --> 00:47:26,000
[UNKNOWN] Čao, bok.

